text: José Antonio Merín (born 11 July 1970) is a Spanish former competitive rower, specializing in double sculls. He competed in that event at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Montsià
